## Transport.dispose() method

Dispose.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
dispose(): Promise<void>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

`Promise<void>`

## Remarks

When the `UserAgent` is disposed or stopped, this method is called. The `UserAgent` MUST NOT continue to utilize the instance after calling this method.
